This paper discusses the technical features and capabilities of 5G New Radio (NR), which is a wireless access technology. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI) category. Additionally, the paper discusses waveform design, coexistence with LTE, and non-terrestrial communications, which are related to Information Theory (cs.IT), Architecture (cs.AR), and Multimedia (cs.MM) categories. Finally, the paper also touches upon the topic of massive machine type communications, which is related to the Computer Communications (cs.COM) category.
